<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es-MX">
  <head>
    <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=AW-17739710700"></script>
    <script is:inline>
        window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
        function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
        gtag('js', new Date());
        gtag('config', 'AW-17739710700');
    </script>
    
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Página no disponible | Delitiāre</title>
    
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow" /> 
    
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0e0f12" />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400&family=Manrope:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

    <link rel="icon" href="/assets/icons/favicon.ico" sizes="any" />
    
    <style>
      /* BRAND PALETTE - Manual Delitiāre [cite: 44] */
      :root {
        --bg-color: #0e0f12;   /* Charcoal [cite: 45] */
        --accent: #d6b86a;     /* Champagne [cite: 46] */
        --text-main: #f6f3ee;  /* Ivory [cite: 47] */
        --text-muted: #9fa1a6;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        /* Actualizamos a Manrope para coherencia de marca */
        font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; 
        background-color: var(--bg-color);
        color: var(--text-main);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        height: 100vh;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        /* Fondo sutil para dar profundidad */
        background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #1c1f26 0%, #0e0f12 70%);
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 480px;
      }

      h1 {
        /* Fuente Display para el número */
        font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; 
        font-size: 100px;
        font-weight: 300;
        color: var(--accent);
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1;
        opacity: 0.8;
        letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      }

      h2 {
        font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 400;
        margin: 10px 0 20px;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        color: var(--text-main);
      }

      p {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        font-weight: 300;
      }

      .btn-return {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 14px 32px;
        background: transparent;
        border: 1px solid var(--accent);
        color: var(--accent);
        text-decoration: none;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .btn-return:hover {
        background: var(--accent);
        color: var(--bg-color);
        box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(214, 184, 106, 0.25);
        cursor: pointer;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>404</h1>
      <h2>Ruta no encontrada</h2>
      <p>
        Parece que te has desviado. <br>
        Esta página no forma parte de nuestra experiencia actual. <br>
        Regresa para continuar con tu sesión de bienestar.
      </p>
      
      <a href="/" class="btn-return">
        Volver a Delitiāre
      </a>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>